Dotfile setup based on Advanced Commandline screencast from PeepCode.

INSTALL
-------
1) Clone to ~/bin/dotfiles
2) Create symlinks:

  ln -s bin/dotfiles/bash_profile .bash_profile
  ln -s bin/dotfiles/bashrc .bashrc
  ln -s bin/dotfiles/gemrc .gemrc
  ln -s bin/dotfiles/gitconfig .gitconfig
  ln -s bin/dotfiles/gitignore_global .gitignore_global
  ln -s bin/dotfiles/vimrc .vimrc


